sources.description:
Following the discovery of a new element that acts as a defense against the atomic bomb, the United Peace Federation sends an agent to Pendrang, the Himalayan province where it was located, to stop warmongers trying to find it.

Directors: Lewis D. Collins, Ray Taylor
Writers: Joseph F. Poland, Paul Huston, Tom Gibson
Cast: Russell Hayden, Jane Adams, Lionel Atwill, Keye Luke
Genres: Colorized, TV serial, Action, Adventure

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/koIuOUda9W8
